videos.headline: Guice breaks multiple tackles for 45-yard TD
videos.description: LSU's Derrius Guice opens up scoring with a 45-yard touchdown early in the first quarter against Texas A&M.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Guice breaks multiple tackles for 45-yard TD) 2016/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trevor Knight puts it in the air for 36-yard TD
videos.description: Texas A&M QB Trevor Knight connects with Christian Kirk for a 36-yard touchdown to even the score at 7.

videos.headline: T. Williams run for 8 yds,T. Williams fumbled, forced by D. White, recovered by LSU D. White
videos.description: Trayveon Williams run for 8 yds to the TexAM 20 Trayveon Williams fumbled, forced by Devin White, recovered by LSU Devin White

videos.headline: Dupre hauls in 20-yard TD from Etling
videos.description: In the final seconds of the first half, LSU's Danny Etlin connects with Malachi Dupre for a 20-yard touchdown to extend the Tigers' lead to 20-7 after the extra point.

videos.headline: Guice takes off for another 45-yard TD
videos.description: Derrius Guice puts on the jets and speeds past Texas A&M defenders for a 45-yard touchdown to extend LSU's lead.

videos.headline: Guice scores his third TD of the game
videos.description: Derrius Guice rushes 6 yards for his third touchdown of the game to extend LSU's lead to 34-10 over Texas A&M.

videos.headline: Aggies fighting back with 33-yard touchdown
videos.description: Texas A&M's Trayveon Williams breaks free for a 33-yard touchdown to narrow LSU's lead in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Chark widens the gap with a 7-yard strike for LSU
videos.description: D.J. Chark takes the ball 7 yards to the end zone to give LSU a dominating 41-17 lead over Texas A&M.

videos.headline: Gage manages to keep it inbounds for LSU touchdown
videos.description: Russell Gage makes a great catch in the end zone, dragging his toes to stay inbounds, for a 9-yard LSU touchdown.

videos.headline: Reynolds scores 32-yard TD as Aggies inch closer to LSU
videos.description: Trevor Knight throws a nice pass to Josh Reynolds who takes it to the house for a 32-yard touchdown as Texas A&M inches closer to LSU.

videos.headline: Guice rushes for his fourth TD of the game
videos.description: Derrius Guice runs for a 2-yard touchdown to record his fourth rushing touchdown of the game and extend LSU's lead over Texas A&M to 54-33.

videos.headline: Trevor Knight suffers apparent injury, helped off field
videos.description: With Texas A&M down 54-33 in the fourth quarter, Aggies QB Trevor Knight is injured on the play, clutching his knee, and is helped off the field.

videos.headline: J. White run for 2 yds for a TD
videos.description: James White run for 2 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Guice runs for LSU-record 285 yards and four TDs in win
videos.description: On the road without Leonard Fournette, Derrius Guice picks up the slack and then some, running for a school-record 285 yards with four touchdowns to lead LSU to a 54-39 victory over Texas A&M.
